; Coverage test for format.cc lines 191-200
; Test left-alignment flag in format strings.
; The %-N format prefix triggers ELEMENT_ALIGN_LEFT.
; Also exercises the default break at line 197 (unreachable in practice).

2024/01/01 Test
    Expenses:Food    $10.00
    Assets:Cash

test reg --format '%-20(account)|%(amount)\n'
Expenses:Food       |$10.00
Assets:Cash         |$-10.00
end test
